---
title: x402 Payment Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as 🤖 Research Agent
    participant Plugin as AgentCore Plugin
    participant CF as ☁️ CloudFront + Lambda@Edge
    participant Chain as ⛓️ Base Sepolia (L2)

    Agent->>CF: GET /mediatech/premium/article.json
    CF-->>Agent: 402 Payment Required<br/>{x402Version, accepts, pricing}

    Note over Agent,Plugin: Plugin intercepts 402 automatically

    Plugin->>Plugin: Validate budget<br/>(session limit check)
    Plugin->>Chain: Sign EIP-3009<br/>transferWithAuthorization

    Note over Plugin,Chain: ~3 second wait for block confirmation

    Plugin->>CF: GET + X-PAYMENT header<br/>(base64 signed proof)
    CF->>Chain: Verify payment proof
    Chain-->>CF: ✅ Confirmed
    CF-->>Agent: 200 + article content

    Note over Agent: Agent reads content,<br/>synthesizes research brief

    Agent->>Agent: Rate content quality
